Farmers harvest sweet potatoes in Zhongtong village, East China’s Jiangsu Province on Sunday. Under the new cooperation model of “Major enterprises + cooperatives + large households,” 3,000 households have seen their annual income increase by about 800 yuan ($113) per mu (0.067 hectare) from cultivating sweet potatoes. Photo: IC  
